README:
This model uses PyGene (http://www.freenet.org.nz/python/pygene/)
or PyBrain (http://www.pybrain.org/) library.

see http://arxiv.org/abs/0906.5127 for details

usage:

make

./optimizer.py or ./PBoptimizer.py

#This script will produce output in file "curres"
#You can use this result for plotting
#For example:

./plot $RANDOM 10 5 0.19 0.16 2.22 27.53 -0.28 17.90 0.20 0.28 0.25

#This produces data file in ./plot/data
#Then you can plot this data with script ./plots/plot.sh

./plots/plot.sh
#or
gnuplot ./plots/all.gpl
